TO COMPILE .java into .classes

sudo javac -cp /var/lib/tomcat7/webapps/fabflix/WEB-INF/lib/servlet-api.jar:/var/lib/tomcat7/webapps/fabflix/WEB-INF/lib/jstl-1.2.jar:/var/lib/tomcat7/webapps/fabflix/WEB-INF/lib/mysql-connector-java-5.0.8-bin.jar /var/lib/tomcat7/webapps/fabflix/WEB-INF/sources/*/*.java -d /var/lib/tomcat7/webapps/fabflix/WEB-INF/classes

SQL info:
user: root
pwd: futurama5

we intended for the user to be able to browse the site without being logged in. They can also have a cart without being logged in. 
If they try to checkout they will be prompted to the login screen.